data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
use cases: alt accounts & shared accounts
instructions:
1) select your steam install directory (c:\program files(x86)\steam)
2) select the account you wish to use as the source of your keybinds. this is your main account
3) if you wish to export or import saved settings and keybinds. do this now. you can stop here.
4) select the account you wish to set the keybinds and settings for.
5) you can now copy the keybinds from account #1 to account #2
important: you must have previously launched dota from both of these accounts to copy or export keybinds.
